Subject: Secunia Research: XnView DICOM Parsing Integer
	Overflow Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 10/03/2010

       - XnView DICOM Parsing Integer Overflow Vulnerability -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

Affected Software....................................................1
